descriptions.value: Underwater measurements captured by a MoLab device (modular ocean laboratory) by GEOMAR, Kiel, Germany

Conductivity time series data (from 2012-06-01T00:00:01Z to 2012-06-01T00:00:01Z). 0 measurements are provided in the JSON format - relative (in seconds) to timestamp 2012-06-01T00:00:01Z. Data was collected in the open water region 'Northern Norway' at geo location (22.4750;70.2681) at a depth of 215.0 m. The measurement unit is mS/cm.
